# Output locale

| Artifact | Language |
|----------|----------|
| Chat replies to the user | **English** (default) |
| Plan files (`.cursor/plans/**/*.plan.md`, `*.brief.md`) — title, overview, sections, todo `content` | **English** |
| Brief tables and AskQuestion option labels | **English** |
| Code — identifiers, types, file names, JSON field keys | **English** |
| Code comments (business logic) | **English** |
| i18n UI string values (non-default locale files) | **Match target locale** |
| `.cursor` instruction files (rules, skills) | **English** |

Override: if user explicitly requests another language for chat, match user for that session.

Full reference: [output-locale.md](../plans/_shared/output-locale.md) and [project.defaults.yaml](../config/project.defaults.yaml) `locale.*`.
